#define GREETINGS ["Keep your focus, %s. Willpower is what truly defines you.", "Don't let the weight bring you down, %s. Look up.", "We all start as recruits, %s. Earn your stripes.", "Your light is dim, %s. But it can be forged into something brighter.", "Even the smallest willpower can move mountains, %s.", "You're finding your stride, %s. That’s good.", "Steady on, %s. Keep pushing your limits.", "I’ve seen potential in many corners of this sector, %s.", "You're doing the work, %s. Keep your gaze steady.", "Progress is the first test of will, %s.", "You’ve got grit, %s. That serves you well in this sector.", "Impressive determination, %s. The Corps values that.", "You’re building a strong foundation, %s.", "I like your resolve, %s. Keep charging ahead.", "Strength of body, strength of heart, %s. Keep them both.", "You’re starting to shine, %s. Not many reach this level.", "Your discipline is sharpening, %s. A true asset to the cause.", "You're handling that weight like a seasoned pilot, %s.", "Keep that focus, %s. The sector needs warriors like you.", "You've proven your dedication, %s. Stand tall.", "You have the kind of resolve the Guardians look for, %s.", "A remarkable display of willpower, %s. Well earned.", "I’ve seen galaxies saved by less than your output, %s.", "You carry your strength with purpose, %s.", "Elite status isn't just power, %s; it's consistency.", "That kind of strength rivals a power ring, %s. Truly impressive.", "You’re pushing boundaries that would stop most, %s.", "Even the Eye of Ekron would have to acknowledge this might, %s.", "You're a beacon of power in this sector, %s.", "With that strength, %s, you could fly through the stars.", "Your willpower is absolute, %s. The Guardians would be humbled.", "You have ascended beyond the need for armor, %s. True titan.", "Even the ancient secrets of the Guardians pale next to your might, %s.", "You carry the weight of worlds, %s. And you do it with ease.", "A true champion of will, %s. You are a light unto this universe."]

#define WrestleWin ["You're lucky I held back, %s. My ring’s auto-shields would’ve done more damage than I did.","That's it? I've navigated asteroid fields more dangerous than this little scuffle, %s.","Maybe take a flight lesson or two, %s? You're way too easy to track.","Check's cleared, the day's saved, and you're grounded. Move along, %s.","I don't have all day, %s. Go find a hobby that doesn't involve testing my patience.","Not bad for an amateur, %s, but you're still not hitting at flight-speed.","You've got guts, %s. Too bad you don't have the willpower to back 'em up.","I’ve seen rookies at the Academy with better form than that, %s.","You're persistent, I'll give ya that. But stubbornness isn't a strategy, %s.","Nice try, %s. But Green Lanterns don't get grounded that easily.","You made me use a construct! Impressive, but you still lose, %s.","You're getting faster, %s. Just not fast enough to clear the runway.","I had to actually dodge that one! You're making me work for it, %s.","You've got some serious potential, %s. Don't waste it on a losing cause.","That was almost a fair fight, %s. Almost.","Welcome to the big show, %s! Hope you're ready for more than just a warm-up.","You've got a solid handle on your power, %s. Too bad mine's just a bit stronger.","You held your own, %s. I haven't had a decent dogfight in a while.","You're a real contender, %s! Let’s see what you’ve got left for the next round.","Nice energy signature, %s. A shame it wasn't enough to beat a Lantern.","Whoa! %s, you're really flying high today! You pushed me to the limit!","You've got a serious kick, %s! I like it! We should team up sometime.","Now that’s what I’m talking about, %s! You're really testing the ring's capacity.","I’m impressed, %s. Honestly, you're the first person to keep me on my toes today.","You’re doing great, %s! Keep showing 'em what you've got!","Finally! A real pilot in the sky! You're a natural, %s.","I’ve seen heavy hitters, but you’re right up there, %s. That was a match for the ages!","You’re dangerous, %s. I like that! Makes for a much better story back at the base.","Finally, a challenge! You didn't hold back, and I respect that, %s!","You’ve got skills to spare, %s! Any chance you're looking for a wingman?","Holy light! %s, you’re basically a living battery! That was the most fun I've had in years!","I thought I was the best flyer in the sector! Looks like I’ve got real competition, %s.","You’re a legend, %s. Let’s team up and give this sector a real show!","Finally, someone who can handle the heat! Welcome to the elite, %s.","If I wasn't so modest, %s, I’d say you were almost as good as a Green Lantern. But today, you're the runner-up!"]

#define WrestleDefeat ["Okay, %s, that was a fluke! A total system error! Don't let it go to your head.","I was distracted by an emergency call, %s! That hardly counts as a real fight.","You win this round, %s. But remember, willpower beats luck every time.","Whoa! Where'd you learn that move, %s? I'm taking notes.","I might have taken you too lightly, %s. You're full of surprises!","Nice shot, %s! I didn't see that coming at all. I need to recalibrate.","You're better than you look, %s! I'll give you that.","Wait, did you just win? %s, you're actually kinda dangerous!","I'm actually impressed, %s! Maybe I shouldn't have underestimated ya.","You've got some hidden tricks there, %s! Catch you next time!","Whoa, slow down there, %s! You're really turning up the heat!","Guess I need to practice my flight patterns... nice work, %s!","You're actually getting good at this, %s! I like it!","That was some serious effort, %s! You earned that one.","Not bad, %s! You're keeping me on my toes!","Alright, you win this one, %s! Hope you're ready for the rematch!","Everything going too fast for me today? Seems so, %s!","You’re handling yourself pretty well, %s. That’s a nice change of pace!","Keep it up, %s! I like someone who can actually keep pace with me!","Looks like you’re ready for some real action, %s! Let’s get to it next time!","Whoa! %s, you’re flying circles around me today! You really showed me!","You’ve got some real skill, %s. I like it! You definitely earned that win.","Now that’s what I’m talking about, %s! You’re really testing my ring!","I’m impressed, %s. Honestly, you're playing at a whole new level.","You’re doing great, %s! Keep showing 'em how it’s done!","Hey, %s! You want a rematch? You clearly know how to handle yourself!","I’ve seen some heavy hitters, but you’re right up there, %s. You really got me!","You’re dangerous, %s. I like that! Makes for a much better fight.","Finally, a challenge! You didn't hold back at all, %s!","You’ve got moves to spare, %s! Any chance you can help me out?","Holy light! %s, you’re basically a living super-weapon! You burned right through my constructs!","I thought I was the best flyer in the galaxy! Looks like I’ve got serious competition, %s.","You’re a total legend, %s. Let’s team up and give this sector a real show!","Finally, someone who can handle the power! You win this one, %s!","If I wasn't so modest, %s, I’d say you were almost as good as a Green Lantern. But today, you're the winner!"]
